Q: https://platform.stratascratch.com/coding/9859-find-the-first-50-records-of-the-dataset?code_type=1
SQL:
WITH CTE AS (
SELECT
    COUNT(worker_id) AS total_rows    
FROM 
    worker
)

SELECT
    worker_id,
    first_name,
    last_name,
    salary,
    joining_date,
    department
FROM 
    worker, CTE
WHERE 
    worker_id <= total_rows/2
